{"tid":470405,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖少字] 魔戒迷紐西蘭之行","createTime":"2017-11-16T09:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T11:30:12.000Z","uid":114088,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"65e6f1f8fec3a96df531ef767ea349d03b0c06c9","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 小弟由10歲果陣睇完fellowship of the ring套戲開始已經成為一個魔戒迷, 好想去親身睇佢拍攝地點, 感受下Middle Earth <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中文翻譯版小說包括精靈寶鑽都重睇左3次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  電影就不在話下啦<br />\n<br />\n本身係3年前畢業後打算去一轉紐西蘭, 但發現唔自駕都好煩, 決定考左車牌先去啦, 咁樣一拖就拖左3年<br />\n<br />\n其實本身都有諗過同(某一兩任)女友去, 但諗諗下都係覺得呢個持續15年嘅夢想都係自己一個去完成會滿足D, 所以直到上年10月同ex分手後即刻出機票, 今年5月成行, 果一刻我爽過唔戴套扑野  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程就用左16日, 香港來回Auckland, 我由Auckland開始揸車玩到去Queenstown, 中途淨係去魔戒嘅景點,有一兩個都幾偏僻嘅我都有去. 由於呢個係魔戒trip, 所以就冇去到Milford Sound, Fox Glacier果D雖然都好撚靚嘅熱門野, 有咩漏左就下次先去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我本身都算係舊登攝台巴打, 曾經跟過&quot;我食玻璃大&quot;撈, 今次個旅行我乜柒器材都帶晒去 (反正有車), 有數碼有菲林:<br />\n<br />\n1. Ricoh GR2<br />\n2. Mamiya M645 + 80mm f/1.9<br />\n3. Contax T2<br />\n4. GoPro Hero 6<br />\n<br />\n(其實都唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nup住3幅相過下癮先, 眼利嘅巴打應該認得出喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/172344_e311993e2192c60c6e31b5371b546580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F172344_e311993e2192c60c6e31b5371b546580.jpg&h=60c0bb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/172346_d16ac2643f553f85eecffe90dc4df9e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F172346_d16ac2643f553f85eecffe90dc4df9e4.jpg&h=56a71877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/172348_294abdaf076736b032ce9581794374c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F172348_294abdaf076736b032ce9581794374c6.jpg&h=7284e25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為返工都幾hea, 所以嚟緊應該每日返工就打一篇更新<br />\n<br />\n待續..."},{"pid":"be93095f594e0a5af4a1e45e0cedc6539d1e45fa","tid":470405,"uid":61970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadf6275304c18117a912c1672c6a1d065096684","tid":470405,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正"},{"pid":"2d8919eb837f400e586ff73aa23482126ce03002","tid":470405,"uid":60960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"魔戒迷留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40096cc5306378876b54f7be6ecff83f213d03d3","tid":470405,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"我女友發夢都想去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841243d89f49c172ed60b7f2e4676a845323b492","tid":470405,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"有冇見到哈比人"},{"pid":"24e7a1ede95ee400ca80973d2fe9f61c4e82d645","tid":470405,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車既魔戒迷留名"},{"pid":"29bb3cdf0d4dc29da2d1376978b91cf5e3f8b80a","tid":470405,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"Where now are the horse and the rider? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9f1c9a7146c809f95551b2e249193b1758dea0","tid":470405,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff1683ae756ce3468575de98994ce3365df2564","tid":470405,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"My precious <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229e879dcebe9fa9bc0263fbb44bc7bc60d59b2d","tid":470405,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意魔戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1981527f07a98e49507c10b1ce788f36a255ec14","tid":470405,"uid":124768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"魔戒既話淨係去過glenorchy, 個度騎馬正到爆"},{"pid":"3199b9288b71415687b24198059d8b282036cb72","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔戒既話淨係去過glenorchy, 個度騎馬正到爆</blockquote><br />\n我有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5c3e1bc4272b1287d28c80c326b27ff1795fb","tid":470405,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e0424fe0bce4b4823da2ce548748cea986cb39","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"好，開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n因為紐西蘭喺南半球，所以特登揀5月去，呢個月份果邊係秋天，又凍又有紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1: 坐CX去到Auckland，過程冇咩特別。一落機就係中午，喺香港已經上網book定rental car，咁到左就打俾間公司 佢地搵人嚟車我去攞車咁。<br />\n<br />\n攞完車都差不多13:30，我預先book定第二日去Hobbiton。其實本身想即日去埋，但佢個tour last session 15:30，機場揸去嘅話google map話要兩個鐘，咁即係一定趕唔到，所以我最終book左第二日最早果場。<br />\n<br />\n揸車一路都叫有驚無險，其實我係2015年10月考到個牌之後冇掂過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次臨去旅行先補左幾個鐘.去到一揸左半個鐘都冇已經喺大十字路口衝紅燈+亂轉彎,差D俾貨車撞,俾人咇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衝完燈一陣又唔小心轉彎剷上膊... 所以大家都真係練多幾下先好去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左呢兩單之外都冇再發生咩事， 上左手就OK， 始終紐西蘭本身都唔多人， D馬路又闊都好易揸。 <br />\n<br />\n我今日嘅目的地係Matamata，呢度係最近Hobbiton嘅小鎮，第二朝一早揸車去都係20分鐘。第一晚book左Matamata唯一(?)一間hostel：Matamata Backpackers Hostel，諗住求其瞓一覺就得。間野都幾乾淨，普通鬼佬style hostel咁，同房有條友係全程踩單車，幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMatamata呢個鎮幾乎乜都冇，KFC M記各一，有2間Supermarket同埋少少其他餐廳咁。值得講嘅係reception條友係英國人，佢話呢度間KFC係全紐西蘭最垃圾嘅分店，連暗黑料理之鄉嘅人民都咁講，所以結果我就食M記算，都成12蚊NZD一個餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後喺supermarket買左D水同零食擺車，咁就返去hostel打機瞓覺。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/143510_63c85d8fea3a65f4a0888e30607c53a7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F143510_63c85d8fea3a65f4a0888e30607c53a7.JPG&h=80b2c7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1 完，遠征距離<ins><strong>149KM</strong></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n揀租車公司果陣都睇左review，終於衡量價錢同還車方便程度之後揀左 Apex Car Rentals，貪佢可以pick up同drop off唔同地點，幾乎所有城市都有drop off point (因為我auckland揸到wellington還車；內陸機跨海去南島christchurch 再揸車去queenstown)。而且問左朋友意見，佢地話最好揀D一兩年車齡嘅車會穩陣D，始終rental car都係俾人粗用 (我自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，而Apex有得揀2015年或打後嘅車，又有audi，所以綜合條件都係最好。(其他有D好平嘅公司e.g. Jucy要揸泡菜車, 而且佢D車油晒紫綠色賣廣告)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得一定要買埋車保險</span></strong></span> 因為我北島果陣遇上落大雪撞凹左車尾，南島去山區又俾石仔剷到架車花晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇保險應該賠死左，而且有保險你點撞都冇心理障礙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0fa4d19750f12878fed009f7cac4ee94ea0385","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思開宗名義話多圖少字結果day 1已經冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為第一日純揸車真係冇影相, 而且機場去matamata呢段路又冇咩靚風景<br />\n<br />\nDay 2開始一定多相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b1ef5b889e6df993607914904a24eb234ac7d0","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Day 2 - Part 1</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n朝早起身即刻出發去Hobbiton Movie Set，可惜天氣唔好，一開始已經落毛毛雨。地圖話揸車十幾分鐘但其實我用左差不多半個鐘，因為Hobbiton本身係一個農場改造成，所以一路入去都好多彎，不過沿路都已經幾有Hobbiton feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到就直接報到，等十分鐘左右齊人就上旅遊巴出發.架巴士會播農場主人同Peter Jackson嘅訪問咁。落車之後就係導遊帶住我地行。<br />\n<br />\n第一個景點就係呢度，俾大家估下係咩：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/105525_9bcf66851b02e8c77bf2df419eb05de3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F105525_9bcf66851b02e8c77bf2df419eb05de3.jpg&h=273182f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/105559_17b1da241beb51afedaac97708f31fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F105559_17b1da241beb51afedaac97708f31fb9.jpg&h=55859709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n就係Hobbit第一集Bilbo一邊大嗌&quot;I am going on an adventure&quot;一邊跑出村個位，上面係Bilbo視覺，下面係觀眾視覺(再前少少)。果陣個Guide仲叫我地扮Bilbo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後繼續行，會見到D哈比人洞穴呀咁，不過好多都得度門，仲有D假嘅花花草草樹瓜菜之類，全部都係Weta班友整出嚟，真嘅一樣。Guide又會講下拍戲D位呀咁。<br />\n<br />\n然後嚟到戲肉了，一路行上山坡就會去到:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/110149_1b20a8431f8ef257292647dee2bdd504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F110149_1b20a8431f8ef257292647dee2bdd504.jpg&h=9ed2a4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^The Fellowship of the Ring入面Gandalf同Bilbo喺生日會前一晚食煙個位<br />\n<br />\n然後.....<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\nBOOM!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/110143_2e07899f443b95b3091627eab2335413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F110143_2e07899f443b95b3091627eab2335413.jpg&h=568b0dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^原來佢頭頂棵樹成棵都係假嘅... Weta Studio用膠造出嚟，連D葉都係逐塊上色，仲要上左好幾層務求似真葉。之後有好多俾風吹到跌左落地，Guide話可以攞走，我都帶左兩塊返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Bag End係入唔到的，冇記錯嘅話都係得度門。<br />\n<br />\n繼續行:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/110154_af2ccd5c3d5311597cd2410a09e9ef0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F110154_af2ccd5c3d5311597cd2410a09e9ef0b.jpg&h=ac008f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^Bilbo 生日會空地。Guide話拍戲果陣真係搞左個Party請晒班local做臨記嚟假戲真玩，仲特登造左隻1%酒精嘅啤酒俾佢地入戲，但都真係飲醉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜隻酒已經飲唔返。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/110744_55738554d92d0358ea9ccf65df90bb8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F110744_55738554d92d0358ea9ccf65df90bb8d.jpg&h=3835030a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/110749_654bfa41d7f35eadf36adcf9ffc6f00c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F110749_654bfa41d7f35eadf36adcf9ffc6f00c.jpg&h=e938a36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/111113_36eac3f4cf217c2a54cb3c9f6e005bd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F111113_36eac3f4cf217c2a54cb3c9f6e005bd6.jpg&h=1c88c0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^Return of the King結尾 阿Sam個窿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/111118_1637a015c51e7e6a3453e0d02bc0a179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F111118_1637a015c51e7e6a3453e0d02bc0a179.jpg&h=85d44424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^Tour嘅結尾係俾你喺Green Dragon飲杯啤酒，只係普通啤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHobbiton就完了，下一part我就會去喺 Piopio 嘅另一個私人農場，果度會係The Hobbit第一集佢地遇到食人妖/俾狼追殺果個取景地."},{"pid":"eeec4e389987db908f14afa6de9b40cda9f42546","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Day 2 - Part 2</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nHobbiton Tour 係11:30完，之後即刻衝去攞車，出發去Piopio<br />\n<br />\n正如上面所講，Piopio有個私人農場喺正Mangaotaki Valley，亦係The Hobbit第一集入面幾個地方嘅取景地。而農場主人都盡量保留左之前拍戲剩低嘅野，整左個tour俾人參觀：<a href=\"https://www.hairyfeetwaitomo.co.nz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hairyfeetwaitomo.co.nz%2F&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=66358c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hairyfeetwaitomo.co.nz/</a><br />\n<br />\n每日得兩場，最尾果場13:00開始，google map話揸車個半鐘，我好趕好趕咁啱啱好到。仲要我果陣係佢冬天完之前最後一日operate之後就放大假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> miss左就真係睇唔到 (就算有我都唔會特登喺呢D山卡啦留一晚，雖然附近有個洞穴睇螢火蟲都幾出名)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/154232_bdef0db5f306c6a9bf358940de84e40e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F154232_bdef0db5f306c6a9bf358940de84e40e.jpg&h=c53b0bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ Mangaotaki Valley<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/154317_a27153ab003d3843549cf19eb6fb1304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F154317_a27153ab003d3843549cf19eb6fb1304.jpg&h=0d18e126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 矮人們+Bilbo+Gandalf打算過夜果個荒廢farm house，但其實大部分野都係用膠造然後搭出嚟。成個farm剩低嘅都係真係木造，有D仲係主人喺倉庫搵掘出嚟真係有好耐歷史嘅農具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/154318_838f0a4e4d04488f79e025dbd02cf0bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F154318_838f0a4e4d04488f79e025dbd02cf0bf.jpg&h=3c2d4aff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 門口，成塊地都佢地嘅。佢地有太多地所以將D 羊就咁放(白色果D)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/155011_5b7e799c946d974998f896d96269a7bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F155011_5b7e799c946d974998f896d96269a7bb.jpg&h=94477408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 佢地搵到兩(三?)把精靈寶劍果個食人妖同都喺度拍，其實只係一舊大石嘅底。把劍係農場主人放喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後仲印左Bilbo第一次得到Sting嘅劇照叫我地扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/155019_7208498b01c7a6d42c4aecee7919e807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F155019_7208498b01c7a6d42c4aecee7919e807.jpg&h=17b6a0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 有冇人認得呢度？<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/155355_2d86b833fcd9dc9b7f74cc88c47290a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F155355_2d86b833fcd9dc9b7f74cc88c47290a6.jpg&h=bc2c8504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後嚟張對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大約14:30玩完，我又即刻飛車去Tongariro National Park(末日火山)入面嘅酒店，Google話車程要大約3個鐘，我果陣驚天黑前去唔到就PK，因為呢個國家好少街燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而最後喺個天仲有DD光嘅時候到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/160213_d729d559375cc4a40536a6ab4ea111c4.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F160213_d729d559375cc4a40536a6ab4ea111c4.PNG&h=e2320380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 2 完，遠征距離 <ins><strong>427KM</strong></ins>。"},{"pid":"66613a33e0f5180622190cff0499f16291291708","tid":470405,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"好鬼正 又全部都綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓豬介唔介意講你總洗費幾多？"},{"pid":"f6ac6454a67255db26d78c52b4e2a1e55489c84a","tid":470405,"uid":43239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:25:43.000Z","msg":"跟玻璃大搵食都唔帶盲俠劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66e2746dd4b400b562bcf91c2fd93cbc0638740","tid":470405,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0f2c77cfbf99b69f411b3ea5fbb1e6bb2fbdff","tid":470405,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"有埋對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329d252b6c06ad6c04742a57f62f92454d823386","tid":470405,"uid":60648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"留名遲d去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhobbiton 同 rohan 既景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樓主一樣都係魔戒迷，原本諗住同女朋友去<br />\n但係而家變左ex，應該要自己一個去"},{"pid":"6d136a716ee14a456a34165bde35b89f8e9b348e","tid":470405,"uid":113483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車既魔戒迷留名"},{"pid":"974d35941ff55f68bc100fb1de93817dabffc11d","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名遲d去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhobbiton 同 rohan 既景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樓主一樣都係魔戒迷，原本諗住同女朋友去<br />\n但係而家變左ex，應該要自己一個去</blockquote><br />\n自己去好爽, 我覺得同唔係魔戒fans去應該去唔到咁多朝聖景點 <br />\n<br />\n一邊揸車一邊播soundtrack不知幾正, 配合埋車外面個景好有冒險feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b6d6f6ab49caaf09a57c20bc13c241257f1df8","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟玻璃大搵食都唔帶盲俠劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n王者之劍係俾我呢D凡人用架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33e51ddfe22a6f2be50102c234c6e5a3bd5be0","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有埋對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後仲多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我會親身入埋鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (上面拔劍已經算算地係)"},{"pid":"00ab6103113937abf7a51986a6b0b64142578815","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鬼正 又全部都綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓豬介唔介意講你總洗費幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我機票用asiamiles換, 所以野加埋應該用左$25000左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左盡量住hostel 之外我冇特別慳, 難得去NZ"},{"pid":"4325b5f11392d4c651fc74d6cd4cc3bda48cafb4","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Day 3, 4</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢兩日好撚sad。<br />\n<br />\n其實前一晚已經問左酒店reception個Tongariro Alpine Crossing有冇開，但連續兩日都因為天氣問題唔開 (Day 4直頭係落大雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，亦成為我依個trip嘅最大遺憾。本身呢條Crossing都成日因為天氣問題而唔開，所以特登預左喺度瞓兩晚就係想穩陣D，點知都係失敗　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway，其實除左行Crossing睇Mount Doom之外呢區都有其他魔戒景點嘅。<br />\n<br />\n首先我揸個半鐘車去Tongariro National Park另一邊嘅Turoa Ski Area，呢度用過嚟做Lonely Mountain嘅入口(Hidden Bay)、Isildur斬Sauron隻手指落嚟果個小斜坡、Frodo &amp; Sam喺黑門前面藏身偷睇果個懸崖 (現實地名叫Meads Wall)，同埋佢兩個蕩失路遇到Gollum果個亂石堆。（Frodo &amp; Sam果兩場其實係同一個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n但由於個滑雪場維護緊，所以我行唔到過去Meads Wall <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只能夠遠遠望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/180859_6ed2facc7a9b2c832020afb5e2fbd7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F180859_6ed2facc7a9b2c832020afb5e2fbd7b9.jpg&h=3d62f052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/180330_cd730acb4666376ca93c13176a9a4e98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F180330_cd730acb4666376ca93c13176a9a4e98.jpg&h=98f56ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/180917_1f477f8c6ae835ca69ab61bc201e58ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F180917_1f477f8c6ae835ca69ab61bc201e58ed.jpg&h=476c57ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n^ 原路因為火山區嘅關係感覺都好荒涼，幾有魔多Feel<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/180922_5c203d3e070123ca80602df4e32e21ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F180922_5c203d3e070123ca80602df4e32e21ab.jpg&h=7027cc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 喺滑雪埸拍好車周圍行下，喺大門口沿住條路行上d 見到 Mount Ruapehu <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果都冇咩好睇咁我就回程食brunch，再去Gollum喺The Two Towers捉魚果條河：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/182238_1bfc29171a0e06a9ba0c0f1618b373c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F182238_1bfc29171a0e06a9ba0c0f1618b373c7.jpg&h=7c78d87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/182023_bd5890549edaf97be4c432e0ab24ac14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F182023_bd5890549edaf97be4c432e0ab24ac14.jpg&h=b981ecd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/182215_002c20ab6986993aa58098a43e9abc42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F182215_002c20ab6986993aa58098a43e9abc42.jpg&h=c934fbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ Forbidden Pool<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/182403_92d919be37fe57a0dda8296c44371998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F182403_92d919be37fe57a0dda8296c44371998.jpg&h=19214681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 本身酒店附近有條好短嘅步行小徑，見咁早冇野做咪行下，點知行左10分鐘就開始落雪，搞到即刻返轉頭(好彩走得快，因為呢度一落就落左30個鐘，我走果日係直頭要封路剷雪)<br />\n<br />\n 之後Day 4我全日留喺酒店，行過出門口望，D雪成尺厚，邊度都唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/183129_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F183129_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=575383d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3 &amp; 4完，遠征距離 <strong><ins>570KM</ins></strong>。"},{"pid":"dae69a14ca1003f7e2f2d14f95de33ade4003ceb","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"補多兩張Day 2相先：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/184337_e94d30c3e6bea76dc76a9b63c8cf173c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F184337_e94d30c3e6bea76dc76a9b63c8cf173c.jpg&h=6e2802ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ Hobbiton<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/184336_0d7d73f8eab6f1f77375dc47d79e05a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F184336_0d7d73f8eab6f1f77375dc47d79e05a5.jpg&h=3c21a264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ 都係Piopio個農埸，Gandalf爆開舊石頭整死班食人妖果個位，但舊石係喺Studio入面用機關拍。"},{"pid":"9ebd788721f2172e429045655de9cee42aee5f63","tid":470405,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"推下先, 樓主無Update 好耐"},{"pid":"abc0aed3082bacdeaf4b49bce6fdeb547291aed9","tid":470405,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b004b4498218b67eec86c6ee17d11edd36ad8142","tid":470405,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"253c4b7c6af6c505e96025f6b797ba1f7a5aec48","tid":470405,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"156ae527569c95cd2c4e708b67840a81b5e8a47f","tid":470405,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T23:20:35.000Z","msg":"推, 一月去紐西蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d62f3b60cb72ae852fd29d777e4a0c0eba71d3","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推下先, 樓主無Update 好耐</blockquote><br />\n去完旅行唔記得左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今日盡量出一篇"},{"pid":"ec7d03cb0a70443f0a75074a516d04e9621b2cbd","tid":470405,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推下先, 樓主無Update 好耐</blockquote><br />\n去完旅行唔記得左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今日盡量出一篇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罰你出兩篇"},{"pid":"3ec9ee00cbab1bd8ae637f1708e3d124b3bba17e","tid":470405,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推下先, 樓主無Update 好耐</blockquote><br />\n去完旅行唔記得左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今日盡量出一篇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罰你出兩篇</blockquote><br />\n3篇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df32480e6559b318fe63dac5f03f08ffd731a17","tid":470405,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推下先, 樓主無Update 好耐</blockquote><br />\n去完旅行唔記得左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今日盡量出一篇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罰你出兩篇</blockquote><br />\n3篇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由佛誕等到聖誕啦"},{"pid":"7326e5325da4cd81e2d1e44af48c8a339f3f36a6","tid":470405,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"Tongariro Alpine Crossing 搵機會再去啦，沿途路標好清楚。行過一次，天色麻麻，但都好靚，主要都係外國人行。雖然有啲辛苦，但都想行多次。"},{"pid":"fb0ff8f95940ba40c7ec1c44474074eee14954a1","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"繼續更新 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Day 5</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實呢日都冇咩好講，由Tongariro國家公園揸車去Wellington要5個幾鐘，我全日就喺架車入面。<br />\n<br />\n一早起身仲係落緊大雪，仆你個街我成架車個頂俾雪掩左，擋風玻璃D雪厚到結左冰剷唔到。。。<br />\n<br />\n搞左一大輪終於開到車門，成對手凍到紅晒　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　之後撻著左車開暖氣，十幾分鐘後先溶左Ｄ，勉強睇到路。<br />\n<br />\n因為大雪關係，有一條highway封路，好在唔太影響我去Wellington。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/161931_db6eacad084b3052d8615bcefae8d1a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F161931_db6eacad084b3052d8615bcefae8d1a5.jpg&h=227a4582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/161948_05a368cb87996397a13ae2ff8a52f8da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F161948_05a368cb87996397a13ae2ff8a52f8da.jpg&h=9f3c1514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162047_7310b3589ab9235de2e751ef5a67304f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F162047_7310b3589ab9235de2e751ef5a67304f.jpg&h=b5ac8d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭1個鐘範圍都係雪景，落左兩日就咁多　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162149_9b08b4df6d5f3c31ad9f54c62137ffe6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F162149_9b08b4df6d5f3c31ad9f54c62137ffe6.jpg&h=6c3050b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162155_180f36029180cab8a97fc72a9f9351b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F162155_180f36029180cab8a97fc72a9f9351b9.jpg&h=c4d278f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162200_9e900fb799162308333202c3c10b5a20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F162200_9e900fb799162308333202c3c10b5a20.jpg&h=0e2b024f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後離開左國家公園範圍就正常返晒，紐西蘭靚到路邊是但一個位都係風景，搞到我成日行兩步又停低影相。<br />\n<br />\n我就係呢一日俾人抄左兩次牌，加埋成$2800HKD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我之後先發現原來D警察淨係星期日同假期先捉人，平時唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入到去Wellington即刻難揸左好多，始終城市入面都係多車多人，俾人抄左兩次牌搞到我極細膽　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162846_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F162846_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=2d977f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 5完，遠征距離 <strong><ins>907KM</ins></strong>。"},{"pid":"40c2a6836e84af90e648ed7d9b7f646b87dc490b","tid":470405,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"出多幾篇啦"},{"pid":"acefc8c70bfc5e060ffd71328968d10606b3db63","tid":470405,"uid":20831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"人在紐西蘭<br />\n留個靚名"},{"pid":"e44b96069cdb99fd8324564e053963a36e88a470","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出多幾篇啦</blockquote><br />\n11月中去完旅行整傷左手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾d時間我打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eb05f01561a679d47ddce382ca9ea70bb635a8","tid":470405,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Day 6 - Part 1</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日相當興奮，首先就係天氣好到爆，嚟左成個禮拜第一日藍天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢日我上網搵左個Full day魔戒Tour，會去晒所有喺Wellington市內+郊區嘅拍攝場地，再加埋Weta Cave Tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/181438_b116a893fa4c3e78a440f42313195e2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F181438_b116a893fa4c3e78a440f42313195e2a.jpg&h=0aa13017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先去Mt. Victoria，據聞當年Peter Jackson就係指住呢個view說服投資人喺NZ拍魔戒<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有4場戲都係喺呢度拍：<br />\n<br />\n1. Get off the road!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/181709_2a5a84a53c12726c3186183bb874c391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F181709_2a5a84a53c12726c3186183bb874c391.jpg&h=45710341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 第一集幾個哈比人俾戒靈追殺，跑去碼頭果個斜坡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 強獸人捉左Pippin &amp; Merry之後要補shot，因為近Studio嘅關係佢地係度求其揀個樹林位扮返河邊果段。好笑嘅係拍戲果日係星期日，正常係會有普通一家大細嚟散步咁，然後突然有隊強獸人喺個幾歲嘅細路面前經過。。。。　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/181707_0c6d91c0362df513dc8e1db6a96800e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F181707_0c6d91c0362df513dc8e1db6a96800e1.jpg&h=33cf7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 俾大家估（下一篇開答案）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/181654_cf2da5bc9ddb915589668bf6e64e3b8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F181654_cf2da5bc9ddb915589668bf6e64e3b8c.jpg&h=ea730a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就去左海邊食lunch，餐廳係劇組演員以前成日嚟嘅cafe，Peter Jackson間屋都喺同一條路(我地架車有經過不過撞唔到佢)，而且導遊話Orlando Bloom同 Miranda Kerr結婚之後都仲特登返嚟食。<br />\n<br />\n食物就普通啦，都唔差，係個View幾靚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/182643_bd34390ee636755557fca15fea553aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F182643_bd34390ee636755557fca15fea553aa5.jpg&h=125b567d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餐廳望出去。間中仲會有企鵝(我睇唔到)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待續.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個tour條link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viator.com/tours/Wellington/Wellingtons-Lord-of-the-Rings-Locations-Tour-including-Lunch/d399-2964001RRT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viator.com%2Ftours%2FWellington%2FWellingtons-Lord-of-the-Rings-Locations-Tour-including-Lunch%2Fd399-2964001RRT&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=b5dd0c40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viator.com/tours/Wellington/Wellingtons-Lord-of-the-Rings-Locations-Tour-including-Lunch/d399-2964001RRT</a>"},{"pid":"cb01a90260bee7ec472a4f0a073274f71c0603e5","tid":470405,"uid":43239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"第一次差d比戒靈捉到個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68a102fa512623904fbac6f0aac51dfd5f8836d","tid":470405,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"Nice"},{"pid":"4b54a03a5395270bb24f698a04cbe72df15fdc63","tid":470405,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nf5f5f5f5f5f5f5f5..."},{"pid":"7f4722e97a89c7673b7d05e309007babb0a509f7","tid":470405,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"有趣有趣"},{"pid":"2f42bb94ae33ac1ce6eb2fc6eef4acde301fd3c1","tid":470405,"uid":46900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}